            <title>[KAFKA-12593] Some Scala, Python, and Gradle files contain the wrong license header</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-12593</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Thanks to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jmclean&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jmclean&quot;&gt;jmclean&lt;/a&gt; for raising this issue in the mailing list thread:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r2df54c11c10d3d38443054998bc7dd92d34362641733c2fb7c579b50%40%3Cdev.kafka.apache.org%3E&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r2df54c11c10d3d38443054998bc7dd92d34362641733c2fb7c579b50%40%3Cdev.kafka.apache.org%3E&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

